creator: Virtuagym Professional
descriptionHtml:
FITclimbing offers you different app versions with training programs, strength and (power) endurance, for sport climbing and bouldering. There's a BASIC version with all main FITclimbing workouts and a PRO version with access to all FITclimbing workouts and the full app functions. Both are suitable for progressive training on all levels. Start now and become a fitter, stronger and more complete climber.

The app includes:
- Options to plan and follow your training activities.
- 3D demo videos.
- High-intensity interval training based on different heart rate zones.
- Over 3000 exercises and progressive workouts.
- Functions to track your progression, weight and body metrics.

The PRO version also includes:
- Options to integrate nutrition in your training program.
- Personalized start-up plan and training advice from a coach.
- Team membership for trainers and coaches.

Select the workout of your choice and play them on your app. At home or in the gym. For climbing and bouldering. Start training for having a lifetime injury free and a balanced climbing life.

PLEASE NOTE: YOU NEED A FIT CLIMBING ACCOUNT TO ACCESS THE APP. YOU CAN OPEN AN ACCOUNT ON OUR 'FITCLIMBING' WEBSITE.
